snippet.title: Warframe | The Second Dream Highlight Video
snippet.description:
www.warframe.com

Ninjas Play Free!

The Second Dream is live on PC, and our latest Highlight Video gives all Tenno a look at what slumbers within...

From a new Warframe, new Weapons, to the secretly guarded titular quest, you will not want to miss this Update!
